Payroll Manager
A Leading HR Consulting Company in UAE
Abu Dhabi, UAE
Posted on: 5 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Our client is a specialized engineering company with over 35 years of experience in engineering industrial market. They are looking for a Payroll Manager having exposure in Regional Payroll Management in a centralized manner.
REQUIREMENTS
Must have:
- Relevant Regional Payroll Management Experience.
- Accounting/ Finance Background
- Good Knowledge of Labor law at least in one of the country in Middle East, with an overall understanding of legislation on payment of Salaries.
- Managed Payroll in a Web enable Environment (Exposure to ERP' s like SAP, JD Edwards, or similar).
- Minimum 10 years of experience of which at least five years should have been in end to end payroll management for a large organization at a regional level.
Nice to have:
- HR Experience (in addition to payroll)
- Experience in Oil & Gas, Project Management, Infrastructure sector or relevant sectors
ABOUT THE COMPANY
A leading HR Consulting Company in UAE.
